FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780315873
OL,3,CStraw flies as shin-kicking champion
OL,4,Ccrowned at ancient rural games
OL,6,FThe rural games mix individual and
OL,7,Fgroup disciplines, including long
OL,8,Fjump, the wooden pillar throw, tug o'
OL,9,Fwar, sack race and running events.
OL,11,FFormer chairman Tom Threadgill said:
OL,12,F"It got shut down for the last time in
OL,13,Fthe mid-1850s because of 30,000 people
OL,14,Fcoming.
OL,16,F"It's been banned at a number of
OL,17,Fpoints across its 400 years."
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@AOUyD@]O]
