FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780315873
OL,3,CStraw flies as shin-kicking champion
OL,4,Ccrowned at ancient rural games
OL,6,FOnce famous for a greasy pole-climbing
OL,7,Fcompetition that would grant the
OL,8,Fwinner a piglet, past games have
OL,9,Fincluded horse racing, hare coursing
OL,10,Fand shooting.
OL,12,FWhile most modern disciplines are
OL,13,Ffriendly contests, the shin-kicking
OL,14,Fbouts ` a staple of the games for 400
OL,15,Fyears ` elicited winces and moans of
OL,16,Fsympathy from the crowd of more than
OL,17,F2,500 spectators on Friday.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
