FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780315873
OL,3,CStraw flies as shin-kicking champion
OL,4,Ccrowned at ancient rural games
OL,6,FCompeting for the second year, Gareth
OL,7,FWay ` aka Gaz ` said: "The kicking is
OL,8,Fnot the biggest part.
OL,10,F"I think that there's an element of
OL,11,Fthe pushing, the shoving. That's at
OL,12,Fleast 50% of, it I think.
OL,14,F"You feel that more than you feel your
OL,15,Fshins."Your shins hurt days after, and
OL,16,FI've got almost football-style socks
OL,17,Fso they hold the padding in well.
OL,19,F"Because of that, the blows aren't as
OL,20,Fbad."
OL,26,@oD@WOUrD@AOUvD@AOUwD@GOU{D@AOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
