OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780315873
OL,3,CStraw flies as shin-kicking champion
OL,4,Ccrowned at ancient rural games
OL,6,FThree-times champion and newly
OL,7,Fappointed stickler Shindiana Jones,
OL,8,Freal name Mike Newby, crowned Andrew
OL,9,FBailey the 2026 winner after he
OL,10,Fbravely opted to compete without straw
OL,11,Fpadding.
OL,13,FUntraditional sporting disciplines are
OL,14,Fwhat make the Cotswold Olimpick Games
OL,15,Funique without falling into a gimmick,
OL,16,Fas Mr Threadgill argued, despite what
OL,17,Fthe name might suggest.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
