OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780315873
OL,3,CStraw flies as shin-kicking champion
OL,4,Ccrowned at ancient rural games
OL,6,FHe said: "When they set it up in 1612,
OL,7,Fpeople were kind of looking back to
OL,8,Fthe classical age so the whole using
OL,9,Fof the Olympic name was very much 'we
OL,10,Fknow what we're talking about'."
OL,12,FIn 2012, the event was contacted by
OL,13,Fthe Olympic Committee ` coincidentally
OL,14,Fon its 400th anniversary ` to feature
OL,15,Fin a London 2012 Olympics promotional
OL,16,Fvideo, reviving its popularity and
OL,17,Fattracting crowds from further afield.
OL,19,FAttendees this year travelled from as
OL,20,Ffar as North Carolina in the United
OL,21,FStates.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
