OL,3,CStraw flies as shin-kicking champion
OL,4,Ccrowned at ancient rural games
OL,6,FThe games concluded with a fireworks
OL,7,Fdisplay and beacon lighting before
OL,8,Fcrowds descended on Chipping Campden,
OL,9,Ftorches in hand.
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
